metadata.description: "Lost City of Etheria" is an immersive Collectible Trading Card RPG adventure set in an ancient jungle city, offering unique NFT characters that can be collected and played in the game. With a richly detailed storyline, breathtaking artwork, and an easy-to-learn gameplay system, players can explore the lush jungles, ancient ruins, and forgotten tombs of Etheria while encountering dangerous creatures and uncovering hidden artifacts.
